---
// AboutStory.astro - Company story and history section
---

<section class="py-24 px-4 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Story Content -->
      <div data-aos="fade-right">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-6">Our Story</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600">
          <p>
            Founded in 2017, Softylus emerged from a vision to bridge the gap between technological innovation and human-centered design. What began as a small team of passionate developers and designers has grown into a global digital agency.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our journey has been marked by continuous evolution, embracing emerging technologies while staying true to our core principle: creating digital experiences that resonate with human emotion and drive real impact.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, we stand at the forefront of digital transformation, helping businesses and organizations navigate the complexities of the modern digital landscape with confidence and creativity.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Timeline -->
        <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
          <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="year">2017</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Foundation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Established with a focus on web development and UI/UX design.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="year">2019</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Global Expansion</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Opened offices in London and Riyadh, expanding our global presence.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="year">2021</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Innovation Focus</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Launched our innovation lab focusing on AI and blockchain solutions.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="year">2023</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Digital Excellence</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Recognized as a leading digital transformation partner.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Visual Element -->
      <div class="relative" data-aos="fade-left">
        <div class="aspect-square relative">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80" 
            alt="Team collaboration" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
          
          <!-- Decorative elements -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-24 h-24 border-2 border-black bg-white z-0"></div>
          <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-24 h-24 border-2 border-black bg-white z-0"></div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Quote overlay -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 bg-white p-6 shadow-lg" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <blockquote class="text-lg font-display italic">
            "Innovation is not just about technology; it's about understanding human needs and crafting solutions that make a difference."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium">
            â€” Aseel Ashraf, Founder
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .timeline-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -6px;
    top: 0;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background-color: black;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .year {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: black;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Touch optimization */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline-item {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  /* Reduced motion */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .timeline-item {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>